{"tid":1464102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我建議聽日記錄航班記錄","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:09.000Z","uid":19623,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f57c50fe2f6837fc3aa00e7c96db81f7ab340538","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"今日發現好多航班原本係取消，但轉為可登機，一切都係機管局同政府陰謀，試下記錄航班記錄，再做文宣將責任還返比機管局，係佢令航班混亂，令旅客無法登機<br />\n例如：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/McxPcoZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMcxPcoZ.png&h=4a4db9da&s={SIZE}\" />記錄時間日期<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊記錄，係政府故意製造混亂 <br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做"},{"pid":"2989271b019a20e9b541f5123d69a5355ef77f6f","tid":1464102,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"要做好文宣同公關<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"26334e548570af178ef7fa1d1f53cf2fb925ccc9","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:27:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0f0b200b78e07af51a533efdcc2b2d184cb3c81","tid":1464102,"uid":68471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">塞旅客一定要塞如果唔係出機場做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n塞嘅話，留返一個counter/閘口出黎，放一條極細既路出黎，由佢地排條好長既隊，排都排一兩粒鐘。其他路block Q曬，咁你就人道了，無位比人入了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍師必缺，你唔使塞死，已經塞死。</span><br />\n<br />\n（p牌狗用曬quota 出post，歡迎大家出post講）"},{"pid":"76345bdec3a2e1306ec0da76346f8754ecf93fca","tid":1464102,"uid":269319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeda11f774b1ef542236a232efcf747ad4704bf3","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ff7c4b5b659dec678469d915333af83d3f02820","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:30:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bf01f3f8852811a079c65c1b842ed7309deeb45","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25c3ed0685e4e25fd5e255261089752a973e6ec8","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"b7d437ff7b44afcd2690e30d9d96f61da00eb1c0","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"793e73895de453a54909ecafc0d78cc2ac563486","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:07.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"0adcd02a2e21c74a51c9bb0f62bd64b05ac464d2","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:41.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"fb2b4d0f49d0eaca9ead73465dfda8dbb0f32b29","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf531bf08394cf382312aae53dec8067922805d2","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9bb911a2bec341089b0c22e8cb65290db5a5195","tid":1464102,"uid":19623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}